In the following subsection, a mathematical model will be derived to estimate the temperature variations as a function of depth. Consequently, to evaluate the performance of the model and compute its deviation from the actual recorded dataset, a set of statistical tool will be used. It comprises of the sum of squares error (SSE), coefficient of determination (R2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
