The coefficient of determination is a measure of the percentage variation of an estimated value. A value close to unity implies excellent fit between model estimates and actual data. It is given by:2R2=1-∑i=1n(yi-mi)2∑i=1n(yi-yavg)2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
